Scope of this licence
---------------------

This licence applies to the textual content and per-trial data files
in this repository (appendices, runbook, README files, JSONL artefacts,
logs).

It does NOT cover:

  - The upstream MCP-server source code at the pinned commit
    (`groundnuty/onedata-mcp` at `08e201b`), which is governed by
    that repository's terms; see `code-pin/README.md`.
